Validation on Register
------------------------

-> first_name 
	- required, 
	- minlength -> 2,
	- maxlength -> 100

-> last_name
	- maxlength -> 100

-> email
	- required,
	- unique,
	- maxlength -> 200,

-> password
	- required,
	- minlength -> 8,
	- maxlength -> 255

-> security_pin
	- required,
	- numerical,
	- minlength -> 4,

-> security_question
	- required,
	- maxlength -> 200,

-> security_answer
	- required,
	- maxlength -> 100,
	- minlength -> 2